Package: TidyChunking
Type: Package
Title: Intelligent Markdown Document Chunking for Text Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for intelligently chunking markdown documents into 
    meaningful sections optimized for keyword extraction and text analysis. 
    Provides hierarchical structure-aware chunking that respects markdown 
    headings while maintaining optimal chunk sizes for downstream processing.
